<xsl:stylesheet version="2.0"
  xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform"
  xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
  <xsl:decimal-format name="d" decimal-separator="," grouping-separator="." />
  <xsl:template match="/">
    <output>
      <xsl:for-each select="/ObjectNode/result">
        <xsl:variable name="product" select="./productionOrder/product/externalId"/>
        <xsl:if test="./department/externalId != ''">
          <cD_Department>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./department/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./department/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./department/name" />
            </name>
          </cD_Department>
        </xsl:if>

        <xsl:for-each
          select="./machine/machineType/departments">

          <xsl:if test="./externalId != ''">
            <cD_Department>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./externalId" />
              </externalId>
              <versionNr>
                <xsl:value-of select="./versionNr" />
              </versionNr>
              <name>
                <xsl:value-of select="./name" />
              </name>
            </cD_Department>
          </xsl:if>
        </xsl:for-each>
        
        <xsl:if
          test="./machine/machineType/externalId != ''">
          <cD_MachineType>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./machine/machineType/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./machine/machineType/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./machine/machineType/name" />
            </name>
            <xsl:for-each select="./machine/machineType/departments">
              <departments>
                <externalId>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./externalId" />
                </externalId>
              </departments>
            </xsl:for-each>
          </cD_MachineType>
        </xsl:if>
        
        <xsl:if
          test="./machine/externalId != ''">
          <cD_Machine>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./machine/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./machine/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <machineType>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./machine/machineType/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </machineType>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./machine/name" />
            </name>
          </cD_Machine>
        </xsl:if>

        
        <xsl:if
          test="./tool/toolType/externalId != ''">
          <cD_ToolType>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./tool/toolType/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./tool/toolType/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <number>
              <xsl:value-of select="./tool/toolType/number" />
            </number>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./tool/toolType/name" />
            </name>
          </cD_ToolType>
        </xsl:if>
            
        <xsl:if
          test="./tool/externalId != ''">
          <cD_Tool>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./tool/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./tool/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./tool/name" />
            </name>
            <toolType>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./tool/toolType/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </toolType>
          </cD_Tool>
        </xsl:if>
   
   <xsl:if
          test="./productionOrder/product/externalId != ''">
          <cD_Product>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/product/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/product/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/product/name" />
            </name>
            <unitType>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/product/unitType" />
            </unitType>
          </cD_Product>
        </xsl:if>

<xsl:if
          test="./productionOrder/customerOrder/externalId != ''">
          <customerOrder>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/customerOrder/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/customerOrder/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/customerOrder/name" />
            </name>
            <customerName>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/customerOrder/customerName" />
            </customerName>
            <priority>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/customerOrder/priority" />
            </priority>
            <deadline>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/customerOrder/deadline" />
            </deadline>
          </customerOrder>
        </xsl:if>

<xsl:if
          test="./productionOrder/externalId != ''">
          <productionOrder>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/versionNr" />
            </versionNr>
            <measurement>
              <amount>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/measurement/amount" />
              </amount>
              <unitString>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/measurement/unitString" />
              </unitString>
            </measurement>
            <customerOrder>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/customerOrder/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </customerOrder>
            <product>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/product/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </product>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/name" />
            </name>
            <priority>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/priority" />
            </priority>
            <deadline>              
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./productionOrder/deadline, '.') != ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="substring-before(./productionOrder/deadline, '.')" />
              </xsl:if>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./productionOrder/deadline, '.') = ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/deadline" />
              </xsl:if>
            </deadline>
            <status>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/status" />
            </status>
            <keyValueMap>
              <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/keyValueMap" />
            </keyValueMap>
          </productionOrder>
        </xsl:if>

        <xsl:for-each
          select="./productionSteps">
          <xsl:for-each select="./machineType/departments">

            <xsl:if test="./externalId != ''">
              <cD_Department>
                <externalId>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./externalId" />
                </externalId>
                <versionNr>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./versionNr" />
                </versionNr>
                <name>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./name" />
                </name>
              </cD_Department>
            </xsl:if>
          </xsl:for-each>

          <xsl:if
            test="./machineType/externalId != ''">
            <cD_MachineType>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./machineType/externalId" />
              </externalId>
              <versionNr>
                <xsl:value-of select="./machineType/versionNr" />
              </versionNr>
              <name>
                <xsl:value-of select="./machineType/name" />
              </name>
              <xsl:for-each select="./machineType/departments">
                <departments>
                  <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="./externalId" />
                  </externalId>
                </departments>
              </xsl:for-each>
            </cD_MachineType>
          </xsl:if>

          <xsl:if
            test="./productionStepInfo/externalId != ''">
            <productionStepInfo>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionStepInfo/externalId" />
              </externalId>
              <versionNr>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionStepInfo/versionNr" />
              </versionNr>
              <stepGroup>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionStepInfo/stepGroup" />
              </stepGroup>
              <stepIdent>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionStepInfo/stepIdent" />
              </stepIdent>
              <stepType>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionStepInfo/stepType" />
              </stepType>
              <stepNr>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionStepInfo/stepNr" />
              </stepNr>
            </productionStepInfo>
          </xsl:if>

          <xsl:if
            test="./externalId != ''">
            <cD_ProductionStep>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./externalId" />
              </externalId>
              <versionNr>
                <xsl:value-of select="./versionNr" />
              </versionNr>
              <camundaProcessName>
                <xsl:value-of select="./camundaProcessName" />
              </camundaProcessName>
              <machineType>
                <externalId>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./machineType/externalId" />
                </externalId>
              </machineType>
              <toolType>
                <externalId>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./toolType/externalId" />
                </externalId>
              </toolType>
              <product>
                <externalId>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./product/externalId" />
                </externalId>
              </product>
              <name>
                <xsl:value-of select="./name" />
              </name>
              <productionDuration>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionDuration" />
              </productionDuration>
              <setupTime>
                <xsl:value-of select="./setupTime" />
              </setupTime>
              <sequence>
                <xsl:value-of select="./sequence" />
              </sequence>
              <productionStepInfo>
                <externalId>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./productionStepInfo/externalId" />
                </externalId>
              </productionStepInfo>
            </cD_ProductionStep>
          </xsl:if>
        </xsl:for-each>

        <xsl:if
          test="./productionOrder/externalId != ''">          
          <xsl:variable name="prodStep" select="./productionSteps[1]"/>
          <machineOccupation>
            <externalId>
              <xsl:value-of select="$prodStep/externalId" />
            </externalId>
            <versionNr>
              <xsl:value-of select="./versionNr" />
            </versionNr>

            <xsl:for-each select="./productionSteps">
              <productionSteps>
                <externalId>
                  <xsl:value-of select="./externalId" />
                </externalId>
              </productionSteps>
            </xsl:for-each>
            <machine>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./machine/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </machine>
            <tool>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./tool/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </tool>
            <productionOrder>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="./productionOrder/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </productionOrder>
            <plannedStartDateTime>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./plannedStartDateTime, '.') != ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="substring-before(./plannedStartDateTime, '.')" />
              </xsl:if>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./plannedStartDateTime, '.') = ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="./plannedStartDateTime" />
              </xsl:if>
            </plannedStartDateTime>
            <plannedEndDateTime>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./plannedEndDateTime, '.') != ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="substring-before(./plannedEndDateTime, '.')" />
              </xsl:if>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./plannedEndDateTime, '.') = ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="./plannedEndDateTime" />
              </xsl:if>
            </plannedEndDateTime>
            <actualStartDateTime>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./actualStartDateTime, '.') != ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="substring-before(./actualStartDateTime, '.')" />
              </xsl:if>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./actualStartDateTime, '.') = ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="./actualStartDateTime" />
              </xsl:if>
            </actualStartDateTime>
            <actualEndDateTime>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./actualEndDateTime, '.') != ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="substring-before(./actualEndDateTime, '.')" />
              </xsl:if>
              <xsl:if test="substring-before(./actualEndDateTime, '.') = ''">
                <xsl:value-of select="./actualEndDateTime" />
              </xsl:if>
            </actualEndDateTime>
            <xsl:choose>
                <xsl:when
                    test="$prodStep/machineType/name = 'Spritzgießen A' or $prodStep/machineType/name = 'Spritzgießen B' or $prodStep/machineType/name = 'Wickeln' or $prodStep/machineType/name = 'Tiefziehen'">
                    <camundaProcessName>Process_Basis</camundaProcessName>
                </xsl:when>
                <xsl:when 
                    test="$prodStep/machineType/name = 'Handmontage' or $prodStep/machineType/name = 'Endmontage'">
                    <camundaProcessName>Process_Montage</camundaProcessName>
                </xsl:when>
                <xsl:when 
                    test="$prodStep/machineType/name = 'QS Prüfung'">
                    <camundaProcessName>Process_Check</camundaProcessName>
                </xsl:when>
                <xsl:when 
                    test="$prodStep/machineType/name = 'Verpackung'">
                    <camundaProcessName>Process_Verpackung</camundaProcessName>
                </xsl:when>
                <xsl:when 
                    test="$prodStep/machineType/name = 'Versand'">
                    <camundaProcessName>Process_Versand</camundaProcessName>
                </xsl:when>
                <xsl:otherwise>
                    <camundaProcessName>Process_Basis</camundaProcessName>
                </xsl:otherwise>
            </xsl:choose>
            <name>
              <xsl:value-of select="$prodStep/sequence" />
            </name>
            <status>READY_TO_START</status>
            <timeDurations>
              <xsl:value-of select="./timeDurations" />
            </timeDurations>
            <department>
              <externalId>
                <xsl:value-of select="$prodStep/machineType/departments[1]/externalId" />
              </externalId>
            </department>
          </machineOccupation>
        </xsl:if>
      </xsl:for-each>
    </output>
  </xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>
